steps.name: Given  **A web browser is at the saucelabs login page**
When  **A user enters the username "locked_out_user", the password "secret_sauce", and clicks on the login button**
assert expected **<h3>** to have text **Epic sadface: Sorry, this user has been locked out.failed**, but the text was **Epic sadface: Sorry, this user has been locked out.**
Then  **The error message "Epic sadface: Sorry, this user has been locked out." is displayed**
